<br>
You got the item you wanted from Ragefire so all is good.<br>
<br>
Someone who helped out with the raid may have really wanted a pair of GoFM.  To shrug them off saying it isn't really important because you got what you were there for can be seen as somewhat disrespectful towards those who may have really been looking forward to the chance of getting the gaunts (and I am sure you do not intend it that way).  I don't think the one dollar comparison really works.  Hell, GoFM are worth more than a dollar on EBay, let alone EQ prices.<br>
<br>
In my ever so humble opinion, I think that as the leader of the Ragefire raid you don't necessarily owe it to yourself, but you owe it to the people who lost out of the gaunts finalization on the issue.  Even if folks say &quot;Don't worry about it, it's ok&quot;.  You can bet a number of them will still be shaking their heads - not that you didn't take action, but that the item was stolen by an unknown culprit and their chance at getting something above and beyond the satisfaction of helping you (which I'm sure is enough) was brushed under the carpet. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F25><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uorala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Orala</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(11/30/01 4:59:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=635.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Adon and the missing loot from ragefire...</span><hr size=1> I saw someone auctioning a GoFM earlier tonight.  It may be just a coincidence, but if you need a name, I can send you a tell sometime this weekend Adon. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uorala.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Orala</A> at: 11/30/01 5:01:45 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#564E39><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ubrendancloudrunner.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brendan Cloudrunner</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#F4CC10>(11/30/01 9:00:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=635.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Adon and the missing loot fro